---
import House from '../images/house.svg'
import Farm from '../images/farm.svg'
import Gate from '../images/factory.svg'
---

<div class="lg:container mx-auto md:mt-12 md:mt-[7vw] lg:mt-[10vw] px-6 bg-indigo-50 pt-16 pb-10 sm:pb-16 lg:rounded">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-4xl mb-2">An insight to our <br/> PRICEBOARD</h2>
        <p class="text-[1.35rem] md:text-2xl font-[300] mb-2">In compliance with KGLSA's standard rates, a minimum of 1500INR <small>*(conditions apply)</small> is applicable for all surveys upto an acre</p>
        <p class="slate-600">Detailed documents issued with all kinds of surveys, and can be re-issued as needed at a later time.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 my-8 md:my-[4vw] gap-8">
            <div class="rounded-md bg-[#ffffffaa] shadow-[0_0_10px_#cccc] px-12 py-8">
                <img class="w-2/5 sm:w-1/4 lg:w-1/3 mx-auto" src={House} alt="">
                <h5 class="text-[1.5rem] md:text-[1.7rem] mb-4">S/HomeOwners</h5>
                <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">1500 INR</p>
                <p class="mb-2">For Homeowners/Small businesses/Public parks etc...</p>
                <p class="text-xl">Measuring upto an acre</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-md bg-[#ffffffaa] shadow-[0_0_10px_#cccc] px-12 py-8">
                <img class="w-2/5 sm:w-1/4 lg:w-1/3 mx-auto" src={Farm} alt="">
                <h5 class="text-[1.5rem] md:text-[1.7rem] mb-4">L/Agricultural</h5>
                <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">1250 INR</p>
                <p class="mb-2">For Agricultural lands/Large businesses etc...</p>
                <p class="text-xl">Measuring upto 15 acres</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-md bg-[#ffffffaa] shadow-[0_0_10px_#cccc] px-12 py-8">
                <img class="w-2/5 sm:w-1/4 lg:w-1/3 mx-auto" src={Gate} alt="">
                <h5 class="text-[1.5rem] md:text-[1.7rem] mb-4">XL/IndustryOwners</h5>
                <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">1100 INR</p>
                <p class="mb-2">For minimal Industries/Large farms etc...</p>
                <p class="text-xl">Measuring upto 30 acres</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-2 pb-10">
            <p class="mb-8">If you aren't happy with our pricing plans or have a different project situation, <br/> give us a call and we would try our best to suite your budget</p>
            <a class="px-8 font-bold py-4 bg-gray-700 text-gray-100 rounded" href="tel:00919446835675">REQUEST QUOTE</a>
        </div>
        <small>* Base rate can vary based on any unexpected hurdles, eg:bad weather/remote and off-radius(15kms) from our offices. </small>
    </div>
</div>